    venueImage:
      "https://ik.imagekit.io/c54qkthzl/0C9A6805%20-%20komal%20fating.jpeg",
    setName: "Retro studio",
  },
  {
    name: "Saurabh Vidyadhar",
    role: "Modelling shoot Client",
    content:
      "I love love love the place.. best for all kinda shoots..especially pre-wedding.. i have done modelling shoots there .. the host is really nice.. the services are great.. most of all the the sets are just amazing .. 10 out of 10",
    rating: 5,
    venueImage:
      "https://ik.imagekit.io/c54qkthzl/5b105eb6-c4fb-4f06-b101-3e71461999a5%20-%20Saurabh%20Vidyadhar.jpeg",
    setName: "Dreamy Walkway",
  },
  {
    name: "Prajkta Talpekar",
    content:
      "We had a great time there, they have best sets available in Nagpur. The owner and the staff are also very cooperative and helping.",
